Viola Katherine Clemmons https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Viola_Katherine_Clemmons 0 Viola Katherine Clemmons, stage name Katherine Dayan, (17 November 1874 – 24 December 1930) was a stage actress best known for her romantic relationship with Buffalo Bill, and for her marriage to Howard Gould which ended in a divorce that was highly publicized in the press.
